{"tid":956442,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎講下你會推介咩港產片比外國人睇","createTime":"2018-12-26T09:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T13:46:30.000Z","uid":9951,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"b51c6763bb70b8dbf325f970c9ca42bb190253fa","tid":956442,"uid":9951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:17:49.000Z","msg":"最近聯絡返個大學識落既鬼仔fd, 問我有咩港產片推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先我知好既港產片大把, 門徒、無間道嗰啲連登都講到厭咁濟, 但我想盡量搵啲較為獨特、而其他國家電影, 什至荷里活都幾乎冇見過既元素喺入面, 又有冇邊啲係睇完之後可以令到啲外國人加深了解現今香港社會既電影?<br />\n自己心水如下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 一念無明<br />\n劏房嗰幕除左可以比佢地睇到而家香港真實既居住環境問題之外, 最深刻係米奇嗰句: 呢度都幾好架! 搬開左張枱都有...一! 二! 兩步架! 完美反映咩係港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 套戲除左余文樂同後期既米奇之外基本上所有出過場既角色都係仆街陷家鏟, 但同時又係現今絕大多數香港人既寫照<br />\nP.S. 記得個導演訪問時講過話套戲個英文名叫Mad World, 想觀眾睇完套戲反思下究竟真正痴線既係余文樂定係佢身邊嗰啲所謂[正常]既香港人<br />\n<br />\n2. 殭屍<br />\n喪屍佢地就睇得多, 但唔知殭屍又會帶比外國人咩感覺呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲記得呢幕喺戲院睇到我透唔到氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/qYPZ3r.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FqYPZ3r.gif&h=7d671023&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n套戲搵個舊式屋村取景又係冇得輸, 加上羅盤、銅錢面罩嗰啲道具又認真, 睇到我勁入戲<br />\n<br />\n3. 車手<br />\n飛車片十套有十套都係鬥快鬥馬力勁, 但車手呢套戲拍到用車黎玩捉迷藏, 我覺得淨係個idea已經值得佢攞獎, 最癲係佢架車90度轉彎嗰幕係零特技零輔助, 訪問嗰時錢嘉樂仲話呢啲基本野佢個團隊個個都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有冇介紹?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7a45bed60b1786357794314b91ddfb80b224a4","tid":956442,"uid":46835,"like":4,"dislike":63,"score":-59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:20:22.000Z","msg":"我諗你仲好後生<br />\n你講呢三部真係唔稱得上係好戲<br />\n<br />\n推介俾外國人睇，真係都要揾返李小龍，成龍同周潤發先得..."},{"pid":"ebd11b4f95c2f42e02a2a0b6c51656dbea6aa8b3","tid":956442,"uid":39012,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:25:28.000Z","msg":"槍火 簡單直接"},{"pid":"2b6d8869443cf041b9089a79b8adcbf0810d5201","tid":956442,"uid":89595,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"de7a45bed60b1786357794314b91ddfb80b224a4","tid":956442,"uid":46835,"like":4,"dislike":63,"score":-59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:20:22.000Z","msg":"我諗你仲好後生<br />\n你講呢三部真係唔稱得上係好戲<br />\n<br />\n推介俾外國人睇，真係都要揾返李小龍，成龍同周潤發先得..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:27:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老未你有冇睇樓主解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家套戲好唔好睇都唔係最主要因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85783dd289bf66df68b83109ff562a36ddc864f0","tid":956442,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:43:08.000Z","msg":"追龍"},{"pid":"b0d4206a8754463ed9b2a57c10ff2b34c350b229","tid":956442,"uid":1440,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T10:08:17.000Z","msg":"十年"},{"pid":"b43547475293e33d276002382e3c4978a724f2b0","tid":956442,"uid":55533,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T10:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/001417_7afd03c97c5c97b6d4743d8d96dc8296.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F001417_7afd03c97c5c97b6d4743d8d96dc8296.jpg&h=e89254d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87b77a70ab2549c16df024d4364a699b87b3e29e","tid":956442,"uid":161731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T10:17:06.000Z","msg":"無間道 暗戰"},{"pid":"591cbf8972b7aaef786c12c6613e46187e2e6a87","tid":956442,"uid":25754,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"cit